request.description:
Get student's notification preferences.

Returns defaults on first call (no 404 — safe to call without setup):
{
  academicAlerts: { classStartingSoon: true, timetableChanges: true },
  examsResults: { newTestScheduled: true, resultPublished: true },
  materialsUpdates: { newStudyMaterial: true, classResourceUploaded: false },
  administrative: { schoolAnnouncements: true, doubtResponses: true },
  quietHours: { enabled: false, from: '22:00', to: '07:00' }
}

Cache: 10 min

