request.description:
Get paginated notification inbox for the authenticated user.

Returns: { notifications: [...], total, unreadCount, page, limit }

Each notification: { id, title, message, type, isRead, link?, createdAt }

**New in v1.0.10**

Student: get all starred resources grouped by type.

Response: { data: { notes: AppNote[], studyMaterials: AppStudyMaterial[], videos: AppVideo[] } }

Auth: STUDENT role required.

Student: star a resource. Idempotent — starring an already-starred resource is a no-op.

Body: { resourceType: "note" | "study_material" | "video", resourceId: number }

Auth: STUDENT role required.

Student: unstar a resource. Silently succeeds if the star does not exist.

Body: { resourceType: "note" | "study_material" | "video", resourceId: number }

Auth: STUDENT role required.

